OL,3,CKnife crime in London: What the latest
OL,4,Cfigures show
OL,6,FKnife crime offences in London
OL,7,Frecorded by the Metropolitan Police
OL,8,Frose year on year in the latest
OL,9,Ffigures, but have not yet returned to
OL,10,Flevels seen before the Covid-19
OL,11,Fpandemic.
OL,13,FSome 14,577 offences were recorded in
OL,14,Fthe 12 months to December 2023, Home
OL,15,FOffice data shows.
OL,17,FThis is up 20% from 12,119 in the
OL,18,Fprevious 12 months, but is slightly
OL,19,Fbelow the 14,680 in the year to March
OL,20,F2020.
