OL,3,CKnife crime in London: What the latest
OL,4,Cfigures show
OL,6,FOf the 49,489 knife crime offences
OL,7,Frecorded in England and Wales in 2023,
OL,8,F29% were by the Metropolitan Police, a
OL,9,Fhigher proportion than any other force.
OL,11,FWest Midlands Police were second,
OL,12,Faccounting for 11% of the total (5,324
OL,13,Foffences), and West Yorkshire Police
OL,14,Fwere third on 5% (2,349).
