OL,3,CKnife crime in London: What the latest
OL,4,Cfigures show
OL,6,FWhen looking at the number of offences
OL,7,Fper population, West Midlands Police
OL,8,Fhad the highest rate in 2023, with 180
OL,9,Fper 100,000 people, followed by the
OL,10,FMetropolitan Police (165 per 100,000),
OL,11,Fthen Cleveland Police (143 per
OL,12,F100,000) and South Yorkshire Police
OL,13,F(110 per 100,000).
OL,15,FThe Met was one of 23 forces in
OL,16,FEngland and Wales to record a year-on-
OL,17,Fyear increase in knife crime offences
OL,18,Fin 2023, with 17 recording a decrease
OL,19,Fand one reporting no change.
