OL,3,CKnife crime in London: What the latest
OL,4,Cfigures show
OL,6,FThe largest percentage increase in
OL,7,Foffences among full-size forces was
OL,8,Frecorded by Avon & Somerset Police (up
OL,9,F24% on 2022), followed by South Wales
OL,10,F(up 23%), the Metropolitan Police (up
OL,11,F20%) and Durham (up 19%).
OL,13,FCity of London Police, the smallest
OL,14,Fforce in England and Wales, recorded
OL,15,F49 offences in 2023, up from 26 in
OL,16,F2022, a jump of 88%.
OL,18,FLincolnshire Police recorded the
OL,19,Flargest percentage decrease (down 26%).
