OL,3,CKnife crime in London: What the latest
OL,4,Cfigures show
OL,6,FThe figures do not include Greater
OL,7,FManchester Police or the Devon &
OL,8,FCornwall force, due to data issues.
OL,10,FSome 112 homicides were recorded by
OL,11,Fthe Metropolitan Police in 2023, 72 of
OL,12,Fwhich involved a knife.
OL,14,FHome Office figures show the number of
OL,15,Fknife crime offences recorded by the
OL,16,FMet was rising at the start of the
OL,17,Flast decade, from 12,485 in 2010/11 to
OL,18,F13,260 in 2011/12, after which it fell
OL,19,Fsteadily to reach 9,016 in 2014/15.
