OL,6,FThe number then began to climb again,
OL,7,Fpeaking at 14,680 offences in 2019/20,
OL,8,Fbefore dropping sharply to 10,080 in
OL,9,F2020/21 ` the first year of the
OL,10,Fpandemic.
OL,12,FA number of factors have contributed
OL,13,Fto rises in police-recorded crime over
OL,14,Frecent years, according to the Office
OL,15,Ffor National Statistics.
